title: Episode 61: Ft French Montana
itunes:title: Episode 61: Ft French Montana
description:
French Montana comes through to "vibe" with the ladies of Lip Service and tells us why he stopped dating a woman after only one week, what names he stores women under in his phone, what his biggest lie is during sex, why ladies are "the new guys," and why he never claims anyone.. Join Angela Yee, Gigi Maguire, Valerie Lora, & Lore'l in this hilarious episode of Lip Service! Make sure you pre order his MC4 album now, it officially drops August 19th!
